overview:
Rohan Pawale is an engineering graduate from one of the most premier universities and majors in Information Technology .

Apart from being an avid blogger and a web entrepreneur , he is a contributor at many authority sites pertaining to blog marketing and SEO including SearchEngineJournal.com .

Holds the position of moderator at MyBlogGuest.com and currently working on his own startup which deals with Wordpress programming and development .
